rong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3528095be43a6790c295bb0264ba8bc9386d2195","tid":1192683,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf879f3ce1c5a963d4e0b6032e9c5eba56ce8853","tid":1192683,"uid":51717,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:58:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">請擅用起底功能<br />\n樓主呢條五毛假膠大家唔好再覆, 亦唔使用佢嘈交<br />\n</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:26:03.000Z","msg":"==?"},{"pid":"bef59e3bd6cc84a9334016a38332f1bdf64a493c","tid":1192683,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a13af78f0fb19b7fc0502a64b33abf828802ef64","tid":1192683,"uid":30788,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"6aa24f32e1b8bb16020112a4c85670c3892d5bc2","tid":1192683,"uid":49329,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:23:40.000Z","msg":"搞分化，返支那啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:24:30.000Z","msg":"<span 